{"title":"linux安装MySql","uid":"d7e17a0107d25252699dec5aba05099e","slug":"linux安装MySql","date":"2021-10-14T02:07:10.000Z","updated":"2021-10-14T22:45:31.599Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux安装MySql.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"MySQL安装\"><a href=\"#MySQL安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MySQL安装\"></a>MySQL安装</h1><h2 id=\"1、安装包下载\"><a href=\"#1、安装包下载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、安装包下载\"></a>1、安装包下载</h2><p>MySQL下载地址：<a href=\"https://www.mysql.com/downloads/\">https://www.mysql.com/downloads/</a></p>\n<p>centos7：下载在命令</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;dev.mysql.com&#x2F;get&#x2F;mysql80-community-release-el7-3.noarch.rpm<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>安装rpm包</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">yum install -y mysql80-community-release-el7-3.noarch.rpm<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>列出所有mysql相关的包</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">yum list mysql*<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>找到mysql-server包进行安装</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">yum install -y mysql-server<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"2、修改密码\"><a href=\"#2、修改密码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、修改密码\"></a>2、修改密码</h2><p>启动mysql</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">systemctl start mysqld.service<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>在mysql的启动日志中找到第一次启动的密码</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">vim &#x2F;var&#x2F;lib&#x2F;mysql&#x2F;mysqld.log<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>使用这个密码登录mysql</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">mysql -u root -p 密码<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>修改原始密码，否则不能进行任何操作 ([] 内可以省略)</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-mysq\" data-language=\"mysq\"><code class=\"language-mysq\">alter user root@localhost identified [with mysql_native_password] by &#39;your password&#39;;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","text":"MySQL安装1、安装包下载MySQL下载地址：https://www.mysql.com/downloads/ centos7：下载在命令 wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;dev.mysql.com&#x2F;get&#x2F;mysql80-community-...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":591,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据库","slug":"数据库","count":3,"path":"api/categories/数据库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"MySQL","slug":"MySQL","count":1,"path":"api/tags/MySQL.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#MySQL%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">MySQL安装</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1、安装包下载</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2%E3%80%81%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2、修改密码</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"ChenJinSong","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"redis安装","uid":"5a4681c603f0c9d9a46ed22467ed2217","slu